data.description: Absolutely gorgeous custom stucco home in the tranquil gated community of Falls at Champion Forest.  The sunny and warm two story foyer with it's stunning wood and wrought iron curved staircase makes the perfect statement welcoming guests into your new home.   The beyond fabulous updated kitchen with Quartz counters, white cabinetry, and stainless steel appliances is gorgeous and the accent color island ties into the cozy family room space with beautiful built ins.  First floor primary suite has lovely hardwood flooring and a stunningly updated master bath which includes a stand alone tub and amazing walk in shower.   There is a study with new built ins and a closet also on the first floor that can always be another bedroom as there is a full bath right outside the door.  Upstairs you have a spacious game room, media room, 3 bedrooms, bonus room and 2 full baths.  Outside you will find a large covered back patio with outdoor kitchen that overlooks a perfectly landscaped back yard.
